<h1>You need to modify the routes</h1>

Use a routes.yaml file similar to this:

<pre>
collections:
  /en/:
    permalink: /en/{slug}/
    template: index-en
    filter: 'tag:hash-en'
  /cn/:
    permalink: /cn/{slug}/
    template: index-cn
    filter: 'tag:hash-cn'

taxonomies:
  tag: /tag/{slug}/
  author: /author/{slug}/
</pre>

And a redirects.json file like this:

<pre>
[{
  "from": "^/" ,
  "to":  "/en/",
  "permanent": true
}]
</pre>
